{"type": "article", "id": 5200, "title": "复古咖啡手冲架", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-14T07:39:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233453g8ICdYa9RPumH3O2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t美国咖啡器具品牌 The Coffee Registry 日前推出了一系列兼具复古怀旧风与实验室风格的咖啡手冲架，选用黄铜、玻璃以及木材 3 种材质制作而成。其玻璃材质的漏斗上布满雕刻上去的波线纹路，采用日本厂商 Hario 的 V60 型号玻璃制成，黄铜支架可以根据不同杯子的尺寸调节高度，搭配以经过涂层修饰的胡桃木材质底座。定价 179－189 美元（约合人民币 1110－1172 元）不等，<a href=\"http://thecoffeeregistry.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233450ZqgXMYybwCHBfJO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233451OXeRKgECtyDFicu8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233451FO9BQgmPTVLKHbh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233452Zc80aBypPND9Jzbd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}